{"h7e2ad6eagf92ag470fgbf06g56a666f48ede": ["Leave m-me alone. I b-beg you.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "440ac2d9-f98f-f0f1-6d58-4a31a11d78e2"], "h787ec430g5cd8g4ac7g8a15g42e989ed40cd": ["Please. I've... I've been through enough.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "440ac2d9-f98f-f0f1-6d58-4a31a11d78e2"], "hedfe4ca6g0eb3g4717g8caag61de91358daa": ["P-p-please. ", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "501235d3-ae78-d68d-2909-c24d23b13211"], "h96405850g10fag4395gb35bgd141877146f1": ["Please. I've... I've been through enough.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "501235d3-ae78-d68d-2909-c24d23b13211"], "hb9807d8bg8d7ag4f3ag973fg651f5f59b1cf": ["P-please. Just leave me alone.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "83776006-5522-a100-7f11-e46cc5937d81"], "h7a4cdcc2gef77g4522ga306ga0adb2ed11fa": ["Please. I've... I've been through enough.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "83776006-5522-a100-7f11-e46cc5937d81"], "hcfc28261ge4d8g4091ga698ge03284f15fc6": ["Leave m-me alone. I b-beg you.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "ea87987f-d718-aaeb-4644-3d33f076f8c1"], "hf4afcb33g3c5cg4a4ag9ea4ge7b10c4354a5": ["By Mordai's eyes, another one.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "f544f3b8-de57-27e7-6b9b-34596646dbb7"], "hbc501ce9g6126g4fbfg98b2gc5d6201a3f29": ["My friend's blood not enough? Come to rip me open too?", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "aa93eb0e-a831-0d7d-f4aa-fcfeeed08605"], "hdfaaaba2g1ce9g4ab0g9b36g8241e2776171": ["I fought for your people at the gate. Show some gratitude.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "3360bd79-f40b-5562-cd8c-d4beb5978de6"], "hab6702cegce74g4956g8e61g080791579679": ["You did not fight to aid us. You simply craved the taste of blood.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "fa884b4a-c058-b293-cce0-a0475890c29b"], "hb1411159g915dg44ecgbeeeg3a73401489c7": ["Speak to me in such a way again, and I will.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "43ea077b-f91f-1f33-7dca-f43da5fb792e"], "h7d81c788g96beg4463ga37bgc14da1162305": ["Leave me alone, toad, or... or... just leave me alone!", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "8f2fbfd4-434e-ceb1-fc36-36d932a9e56c"], "hdd0b1412gf2f8g4b41g8577g306896f3e6c0": ["You've seen other githyanki? Tell me where - or I'll have your head.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "7bc52d43-4e8d-ef9d-2691-9fb38e2828d9"], "h8359d915g9515g46b6gaa8eg8b28556b3eed": ["I'll t-tell you. Just stay back, all right?", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "8bfda13e-5121-0e7e-b0cf-82fc2e5231b7"], "h588f5ddeg31b3g46cagbb86g6cef84ef7839": ["They were on the road to Baldur's Gate, near the mountain p-pass.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "c60d6ae7-f983-9fec-75b8-86ad34ead4a7"], "ha32d27c6ga728g4d0cga93eg4063e2b35f50": ["It saw <i>us</i> 'fore we saw <i>it.</i> Jammed its blade through Yul's belly, straight to the other side.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "4a13bce0-1776-3beb-914c-7731390c45c2"], "h9dd3c739ged7eg425bgb397g6b1ba7907b9b": ["And I just... I just <i>ran.</i>", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "ac2f9050-77bb-f2b8-d4f5-2d0a23a0eb2a"], "h61e1ec9dg5cceg4373gbcd7g6cccf3cdf82e": ["Now get away from me!", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "72957c93-d02f-ca6c-19cc-ca44e6d5c824"], "he36771fbg5669g475egaea9g349cc50346c6": ["Stand back, toad. I owe you nothing!", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "91400052-9cab-e95b-20be-8f89f7ad2b8a"], "h755ee59cg46f3g46e4gbe0ag52132c7c37ac": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "8d9a8b74-42c9-70fb-2dfa-ad3606fe0345"], "h80f6a0f8g3d2fg427bg8512g74ec6e919176": ["How long d'you think we've got before the goblins come?", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "1ba9ced2-27ac-7fac-1c0f-6e1699240224"], "hdfdb8df1gbca7g4e17gb777g4a0e043890f8": ["We should be getting drunk, at least. It's no fun waiting for death sober. ", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_TieflingGuard11.html", "7030cfc6-17b8-04f1-97c5-91863cb08190"]}